    <item>
      <title>美国将新日铁终止美国钢铁竞标的最后期限延长至 6 月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/us-extends-deadline-for-nippon-steel-to-end-us-steel-bid-to-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国钢铁公司发表的声明称，美国外国投资委员会批准延长新日本制铁公司放弃以 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司的最后期限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/us-extends-deadline-for-nippon-steel-to-end-us-steel-bid-to-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 03:56:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市低迷，开局创 2016 年以来最差</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/china-stocks-gripped-by-gloom-in-worst-start-to-year-since-2016</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一种熟悉的悲观情绪正在中国股票投资者心中重现，地缘政治风险的上升暗示着，在令人失望的新年开局之后，市场将面临更多麻烦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/china-stocks-gripped-by-gloom-in-worst-start-to-year-since-2016</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>强劲的就业数据将推动美国通胀推动美联储暂停加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/us-inflation-is-set-to-back-fed-pause-after-robust-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在就业市场强劲、经济稳健的背景下，美国潜在通胀在 2024 年底可能仅会略有降温，从而支持美联储采取缓慢进一步降息的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/us-inflation-is-set-to-back-fed-pause-after-robust-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>实物支付债务风险不断增加，引发监管机构审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/growing-risks-from-pik-draw-watchdog-scrutiny-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织 (IMF) 计划深入研究日益盛行的实物支付债务，这种债务允许企业推迟支付利息，因为人们普遍担心这种工具可能通过掩盖压力来破坏金融稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/growing-risks-from-pik-draw-watchdog-scrutiny-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛杉矶大火向东北蔓延，威胁贝莱尔和布伦特伍德</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/weather-set-to-heighten-los-angeles-fire-risks-after-respite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[毁灭性的帕利塞兹大火向东北方向推进，在短暂的喘息之后，更多干燥风的威胁加剧了风险，迫使南加州极其富裕的布伦特伍德和贝莱尔社区重新进行疏散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-11/weather-set-to-heighten-los-angeles-fire-risks-after-respite</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 11 Jan 2025 12:13:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ESG 反对者在美国航空 401(k) 诉讼案中取得新胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/esg-opponents-get-novel-win-in-american-airlines-401-k-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，德克萨斯州一名联邦法官裁定，美国航空公司将追求环境、社会和公司治理目标的投资公司的资金注入其 401（k）计划，违反了联邦法律，这是该战略反对者迄今为止取得的最大胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/esg-opponents-get-novel-win-in-american-airlines-401-k-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 18:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
